Rating: 4
Other than halving the recipe (fits beautifully in a 9" pyrex pie plate), I made it exactly as printed. Thought it was mah-velous! Tart and sweet and bursting with flavor. Used fresh rhubarb and strawberries. While it would be even better with premium vanilla ice cream, at Passover, beggers can't be choosers. Might try a creme anglais next year. A keeper.

